NOTE THAT YOU CAN NOT USE THIS AS A PACKAGE VIA LIBRARY() OR REQUIRE() AS OF YET, BUT WE ARE WORKING ON GETTING THERE. 


This set of functions/package will access DataCite metadata using their OAI-PMH harvester. 

This is a public service, so no need for an API key or anything like that. 

Documentation for the DataCite OAI-PMH: http://oai.datacite.org/

Documentation for OAI-PMH in general: http://www.openarchives.org/OAI/openarchivesprotocol.html